d in parenthetical headings in italics above the applicable disclosure or within the applicable disclosure for each", "bbox": [85.4, 1206.6, 1091.8, 1229.8]}, {"text": "Registrants' related activities and disclosures. Within combined disclosures, amounts are disclosed for any Registrant when", "bbox": [85.4, 1231.7, 1117.0, 1254.8]}, {"text": "significant.", "bbox": [85.4, 1256.7, 178.8, 1279.8]}, {"text": "Business and Consolidation", "bbox": [85.4, 1306.5, 342.5, 1329.8]}, {"text": "(PPL)", "bbox": [85.4, 1356.7, 141.5, 1379.8]}, {"text": "PPL is a utility holding company that, through its regulated subsidiaries, is primarily engaged in: 1) the distribution of", "bbox": [85.4, 1406.7, 1074.3, 1429.8]}, {"text": "electricity in the U.K.; 2) the generation, transmission, distribution and sale of electricity and the distribution and sale of natural", "bbox": [85.4, 1431.7, 1151.0, 1454.8]}, {"text": "f", "bbox": [1081.1, 1431.7, 1088.1, 1454.8]}, {"text": "gas, primarily in Kentucky; and 3) the transmission, distribution and sale of electricity in Pennsylvania. Headquartered in", "bbox": [85.4, 1456.7, 1102.3, 1479.8]}, {"text": "Allentown, PA, PPL's principal subsidiaries are PPL Global, LKE (including its principal subsidiaries, LG&E and KU) and", "bbox": [85.4, 1481.7, 1117.7, 1504.9]}, {"text": "PPL Electric. PPL's corporate level financing subsidiary is PPL Capital Funding.", "bbox": [85.4, 1506.7, 763.6, 1529.9]}]}